ican team-mates shouted for her to come back.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999983838321768, \"rank\": 8.599847918691606e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"camera shot\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles looked a little embarrassed as she realised her mistake and shared a joke with her team-mates before lining up for a deafening introduction.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"her mistake\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"a joke\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"her team-mates\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"a deafening introduction\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She has not been in the competition arena for a while and forgets to salute the crowd,' BBC commentator Matt Baker said.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9633914486428139, \"rank\": 0.022513942930493223, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"score\": 0.9803545262362454, \"rank\": 0.01665365599791718, \"text\": \"Matt Baker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition arena\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1096